<translation id="264609280318319531">Cobalt - Amasayithi aphakanyisiwe</translation>
<translation id="628445239225255562">Ukuze uqhubeke nokusebenzisa le wijethi, phansi esikrinini, thepha okuthi Hlela, ibe usuthepha +. Iya ku-Cobalt bese ukhetha Izinqamuleli ze-Cobalt.</translation>
</translationbundle>